{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "胡铁花再入黑暗山窟，误把楚留香当成鬼影连番交手，才知原随云借火折子和地形诱他误判。楚留香判断原随云未必逃出洞外，转而等待破局。黑衣蒙面人抱着受伤的金灵芝现身，外面众人似已惨死，随后“东三娘”和高亚男诈死突袭，被神秘女子阻止。黑衣人揭面为华真真，洗清胡铁花对她的误会；楚留香进一步揭出真正凶手竟是枯梅大师，她甚至可能才是蝙蝠岛暗中主使。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论你是人是鬼，你都休想跑得了!",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "小胡，你已把我鼻子都撞歪了，还不够么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我只当真的见了鬼，原来是你这老臭虫!我问你，方才你为什么不开腔?为什么要逃?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我看你才真的见鬼了，我好好站在这里，是你自己撞上来的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你一直站在这里?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我刚走过来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "刚才和我交手的那个人不是你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我几时和你交过手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那……那么刚才那个人呢?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "刚才有个人就从这里逃走的，你不知道?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你在做梦么?这里连个鬼都没有，哪里有人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这次我真遇见了鬼?……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你究竟是谁?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你连我的声音都听不出?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "连眼睛看到的事都未必是真的，何况耳朵?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你现在好像真的学乖了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若真是老臭虫，火折子呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "在呀?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，点着它，让我看看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "看什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "看你!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你总得先放开我的手，我才能……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论你是人是鬼，这次我都要打出你的原形来让我瞧瞧!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你还等什么，有种就过来，谁怕了你?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你当然不怕我，只不过，我倒真有点怕你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是你?你……你什么时候来的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你跟我说了半天话，几乎将我一个脑袋打成两个，现在，居然还问我是什么时候来的?除了你还有谁能做得出这种事?我不怕你怕谁?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我又不是要打你，你刚刚不是还在那边么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你打的就是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我打的若是你，那人是谁呢?他怎么也有个火折子?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那边就是出口，他莫非已逃到外面去了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这次，你好像总算说对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既然知道是他，为什么不追?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我本来是想去追的，只可惜有个人拉住了我的手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他是个瞎子，我怎么想得到他身上会带着火折子?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "谁规定瞎子身上不能带火折子的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他带火折子有什么用?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他带火折子的确没什么用，也许只不过为了要你这种人打老朋友而已。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论如何，我总没有碰坏你一根汗毛，可是你呢?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我怎么样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在还不去追他，还在这里臭你的老朋友——我那拳就算真打着你，也不会打死你的，但我却已经快被你臭死了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "现在就算去追，也追不着的，阴天打孩子，闲着也是闲着，有人可以臭臭总比呆站着的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "除了臭人外，你已经没有别的事好做了么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我还有什么好做的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "张三、高亚男、英万里，这些人全都在外面，现在原随云既然已溜出去了，你还有心情在这里胡说八道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "除了张三他们，外面还有没有别的人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "当然还有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "还有多少人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "至少也有二十来个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "既然还有二三十个人在外面，原随云一个人敢出去么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "若是还没有出去，到哪里去了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我怎么知道?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不知道谁知道?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "谁都不知道，这里是他的窝，老鼠若是已藏入自己的窝，就算再厉害的猫，也一样找不着的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "找不着难道就算了?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我听说回教的经典上有句话说：山若不肯到你面前来，你就走到山前面去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是什么意思?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这意思就是说，我若找不到他，就只有等他来找我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就站在这里等?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "反正别的地方也不见得比这里好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他若不来呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你难道还有什么别的好法子?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一个人的腕子若是脱了臼，不知道疼不疼?",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "疼不疼都是我的事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你不想接上去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我要接的话我自己会接，用不着你来烦心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "既然你自己会接，还等什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老实说，我已被你气得发晕，根本已忘了这回事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "金灵芝呢?你还没有找到她?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我找了半天，根本连个人影都没有看到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但我却看到了个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我虽然没有真的看到他，却听到了他的咳嗽声，还被他的手摸了一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你既然没有真的看到他，又怎知他是人?还是鬼?……莫非，又有个女鬼看上了你?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若要在这里等，就一个人等吧!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我……我去找。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你能找得到?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我要找的人又不只原随云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "还有金姑娘、华真真?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道华真真对你好像不错，你好像也看上了她，可是你现在总该知道，主谋害死枯梅大师的就是她，杀死白猎的也是她，她干的坏事简直比原随云还要多，你难道还想护着她?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在我只有一件事还不明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "想不到你居然也有不明白的事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我想不通她是怎么会认得原随云的?和原随云究竟有什么关系?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她当然认得原随云，你也认得原随云的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但她却早就认得了，否则为什么要将清风十三式的心法盗出来给他呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认得这人?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "幸亏认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他究竟是谁?你在这里怎么会有别的朋友?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他不是别的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "金姑娘受了伤?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "伤得重不重?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "别的人呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "好，既然如此，我们先出去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她也许还有救，你怎么还慢吞吞的?……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_gao_ya_nan",
      "text": "你……你怎会做出这种事来的?你疯了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "东三娘又为了什么要向你下毒手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她不是东三娘!",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你早已看出她不是东三娘?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我……我只是在怀疑。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知道她是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她是谁，你永远都不会想得到的!",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她就是凶手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么我也知道她是谁了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦!",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "华真真，她一定就是华真真。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她一定不是华真真。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "她不是谁是?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "华真真",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你要找的金姑娘，我已经替你找来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "世界上的事有时的确很奇妙，你认为最不可能发生的事，却往往偏偏就会发生……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你认为谁最不可能是凶手呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "枯梅大师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，就算她还没有死，无论谁也不可能想到凶手是她。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    }
